  "text": "We used object outlines in the city of Porto, Portugal, summarized in Table III and described in detail in [CITATION_1] . A snapshot of the data is shown in Fig. 4 . We also used the building and foliage outlines from OpenStreetMap [CITATION_2] . [CITATION_3] Since the separation of measured data into LOS, NLOSv, and NLOSb links was done manually (by watching videos), there might exist occasional classification errors (e.g., while transitioning from one link type into another). ",
